data.description: Two single family houses on a single lot, 100% tax abated until 2028. 1424 E Rich (1,506 SF) is a fully renovated 3 bedroom, 3 full bathroom Italianate featuring top of the line finishes and full stainless appliance package including beverage cooler. 1426 E Rich (934 SF) is 2 full bedroom, 1 full bathroom and could benefit from cosmetic improvements offering a value add opportunity surrounded by luxury new builds and renovated properties. The site is walkable within 10 minutes to the Franklin Park Conservatory and new vendors at the Trolley Barn. Both houses occupied, please do not disturb residents. *See A2A*
